{"data":[{"id":559464827,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"e70a63b643b51ff44db0229713301d53","url_token":"du-shi-tao-lu","name":"都是套路","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/03b42d62450ffcb05428b958512bea22_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/03b42d62450ffcb05428b958512bea22_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/e70a63b643b51ff44db0229713301d53","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":1,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559464827","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545729199,"updated_time":1545729199,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":10,"comment_count":2,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e这个问题让我想到了知乎之前一个提问：＂有1000W现金算有钱人吗？＂\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e哥德巴赫猜想和1000W在你们眼中应该都有相当的高度，但你们对他们真正的分量一无所知。这么说吧，很多资产上10亿的人都未必有1000万现金流（当然也有人偶然得到1000W现金，比如中彩票、房屋拆迁补偿等情况）；而哥德巴赫猜想也远远不像它本身看起来那么简单而人畜无害。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e回到问题本身，从假设出发确实可以推出结论：如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，绝对可以上清华北大。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e为什么大多数人觉得这句话不对呢，因为你的假设和结论都不靠谱。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e先说假设：如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想。高中生有没有可能证明哥德巴赫猜想呢？有可能。许多天才数学家都是年少成名，比如伽罗瓦、舒尔茨。但他们都是接受过严格的数学体系训练的，远不止高中生水平。我们假设你是用初等方法证明了哥德巴赫猜想（因为如果高中生已经系统学习过高等数学《不只是大学的高数》到能够证明哥德巴赫猜想需要的地步，大概率早已出名），那么有99.999999％是错误的，当然你也有可能是剩下的那0.000001％。此处没有任何打击或者贬低的意思，只是因为哥德巴赫猜想太难而许多民科试图用初等方法证明，导致大多数人根本不相信仅仅使用初等数学能够证明哥德巴赫猜想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以假设成立的可能性太低太低。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e再说结论：能上清华北大吗？当然能。可以但没必要。别说上清华北大了，就是你想去清华北大执教也完全没有问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后，人不轻狂枉少年，数学需要天才想法，年纪轻轻硕果累累的数学家比比皆是。如果你真的证明出来了（哪怕是用初等方法），被主流数学界承认（而不是类似于民科间的互嗨），那么怎么称赞你都不为过，至少也是超越陈景润的存在；如果被其他人指出来是错误的，也希望你大方接受，没有人会因此而看不起你，毕竟证明错误实在是太正常了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后的最后，搞学术没有捷径，就算上了清华北大还是要踏踏实实地学习。人生需要仰望星空，更需要脚踏实地。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"这个问题让我想到了知乎之前一个提问：＂有1000W现金算有钱人吗？＂哥德巴赫猜想和1000W在你们眼中应该都有相当的高度，但你们对他们真正的分量一无所知。这么说吧，很多资产上10亿的人都未必有1000万现金流（当然也有人偶然得到1000W现金，比如中彩票、房…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=337\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomm